    "description": "The UniMate USB/TRRS (Audio Port) PKI token is a hardware cryptographic module. It provides digital signature generation/verification for online authentications and data encryption/decryption for online transactions. The user's private and public key pairs can be generated and stored on the embedded chip within the UniMate cryptographic module. The private key can never be exported. UniMate provides the USB interface and audio port (TRRS) that can connect the module to a computer and smart mobile device. The UniMate implements type A USB 1.1 specifications and USB CCID protocol.",
